    "body": "I still got the deadline when modifying the code like this:\r\n```go\r\n// ProxyRequest proxies the request to grpc-gateway.\r\nfunc (m *ApiProxyMiddleware) ProxyRequest(req *http.Request) (*http.Response, ErrorJson) {\r\n\t// In case we are proxying event stream requests, we do not set an HTTP timeout.\r\n\ttimeout := m.Timeout\r\n\tif req.Header.Get(\"Content-Type\") == \"text/event-stream\" {\r\n\t\ttimeout = time.Duration(0)\r\n\t}\r\n```\r\nMaybe i need to do the same in multiple places of the api middleware?",
