    "body": "The reason why this change does not work is because the grpc-gateway server still times out.\r\nhttps://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/16bbf5602fc1b0756c4e2e61cfcb220a85de117b/api/gateway/options.go#L87-L93\r\nFrom the perspective of Beacon APIs, we can remove this part because grpc-gateway endpoints are marked as `/internal` and everyone should use the non-internal paths. But from the perspective of Prysm APIs, this will make the `--api-timeout` flag not do anything, because Prysm APIs rely solely on grpc-gateway. To resolve this we can potentially register two grpc-gateway servers, one for each API.",
